OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSafety plea over           
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fco-sleeping baby deaths    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffigures                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents are being urged to heed advice 
OL,6, on co-sleeping with babies after new   
OL,7, infant death figures were released.    
OL,9,FBBC News has learned that more than a  
OL,10,Fquarter of infant deaths in Scotland   
OL,11,Flast year involved co-sleeping.        
OL,13,FThe NHS no longer tells parents never  
OL,14,Fto bedshare with their babies but      
OL,15,Ffocuses advice on doing so more safely.
OL,17,FSolicitor general, Ruth Charteris KC,  
OL,18,Fsaid the figures suggested some babies 
OL,19,Fwere dying in "high-risk" co-sleeping  
OL,20,Fsituations.                            
